Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.10,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.01,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,lt's all your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.83,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Huh? ''Atonement memo''?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:35.87,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,''Drags Madoka Yuki in at the infirmary.''
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:40.57,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,''Sold for a hundred dollars an\Nhour in the Chemistry Prep Room.''
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.74,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:58.79,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,l'm so happy you came\Nto visit me at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.15,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Where's Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.96,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,She's been in her room since she\Ncame home, and won't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:09.19,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,l think something might\Nhave happened at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.23,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Nanase, do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:13.81,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:14.71,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.55,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Oh, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.48,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,lt's my homework. lt's a research paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.71,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,l'll go make some tea. Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:51.51,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,ATONEMENT NEWSPAPER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:56.75,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Atonement Newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.02,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,You and your sister were writing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:01.49,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.58,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,You've hit the nail right on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:10.46,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Why did you write a paper like that? Why\Ndid you put in the fact that l've been raped?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.56,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,You want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:14.60,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Of course l do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.57,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Our father's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.44,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,...is Takahiro Nishino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:36.36,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,My father and your father, Koji\NHiramatsu, were classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:44.02,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,At that time, the Atonement Newspaper\Nwas circulating the school secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.20,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,My father wrote and circulated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:53.61,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,My father couldn't bring himself\Nto do the abominable things\Nthat your father was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:22:01.38,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,So instead, he disclosed the truth, and\Nenjoyed watching your father panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:08.74,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,My father was laid off from his company\Na year ago, and he needed money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:12.76,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,With this economy, he\Ncouldn't find another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:17.76,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,lt got to the point that we were\Nstruggling just to pay our living\Nexpenses and the mortgage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:20.87,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,WEEKLY RESOURCE\NSPECIAL REPORT: THE REVOLUTIONARIES\NOF THE EDUCATION WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:24.61,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,WEEKLY RESOURCE\NSPECIAL REPORT: THE REVOLUTIONARIES\NOF THE EDUCATION WORLD\NAnd he just happened to find out\Nabout Koji, after about ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:24.97,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,WEEKLY RESOURCE\NSPECIAL REPORT: THE REVOLUTIONARIES\NOF THE EDUCATION WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:30.01,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,He had succeeded in running\Nhis own Cram School, and was\Ngetting noticed by the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.31,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,WEEKLY RESOURCE/SPECIAL REPORT: THE\NREVOLUTIONARIES OF THE EDUCATION WORLD\NHOW IS HE GOING TO CHANGE\NJAPAN'S FUTURE!? - AKAWA\NMEDIA TAKES NOTICE: KOJI HIRAMATSU\NTHE THREAT OF THE EDUCATIONAL\NSYSTEM'S COLLAPSE. SOMETHING\NMUST CHANGE! - YAMAMOTO\NHe had succeeded in running\Nhis own Cram School, and was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:31.91,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,WEEKLY RESOURCE/SPECIAL REPORT: THE\NREVOLUTIONARIES OF THE EDUCATION WORLD\NHOW IS HE GOING TO CHANGE\NJAPAN'S FUTURE!? - AKAWA\NMEDIA TAKES NOTICE: KOJI HIRAMATSU\NTHE THREAT OF THE EDUCATIONAL\NSYSTEM'S COLLAPSE. SOMETHING\NMUST CHANGE! - YAMAMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:32.75,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,MEDIA TAKES NOTICE: KOJI HIRAMATSU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:35.02,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,MEDIA TAKES NOTICE: KOJI HIRAMATSU\NMy father used the evidence from\NKoji's past to get some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.95,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,My father used the evidence from\NKoji's past to get some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.59,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,But as they were talking, Koji\Nfound out that my dad wrote\Nthe Atonement Newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.99,0:22:45.22,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,ln a rage, Koji murdered my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:47.79,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Leaving us behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:57.57,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,We found out everything when\Nwe were cleaning up my father's\Nkeepsakes, and found his note.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:05.61,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,We couldn't forgive Koji. He had to be\Nbrought to justice, but that wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:09.31,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,We decided to punish\Nhim by tormenting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:12.51,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,...by publishing the same\NAtonement Newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:20.55,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Thank you for telling me everything.\Nl hope l never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:22.89,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:25.79,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:28.70,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,There's one more important\Nthing l need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:30.63,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:36.90,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,The student your father raped when he\Nwas a teacher, her last name was Ohbari.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:38.90,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Ohbari?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:40.58,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:45.11,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,lt's the same last name as\Nthe ringleader of the group of\Nguys that's been raping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:51.95,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,l accidentally found this out\Nmyself, when l was investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.35,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,He's your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.23,0:23:56.79,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.70,0:24:36.23,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,You didn't have sex with\Nme...because we're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.04,0:24:41.67,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Why did you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:45.41,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,How could you do something\Nso terrible to your own sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.15,0:24:52.28,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what kind of pitiful\Nlife my mother and l had to live,\Ncompared to you and your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.45,0:24:56.85,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,That guy murdered\Nsomeone and got arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:24:58.16,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,He dug his own hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.69,0:25:00.68,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,lt's too bad that he\Ncommitted suicide, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.90,0:25:04.33,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,And who was going to\Ntake revenge on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.00,0:25:06.69,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,My mother got sick and died!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.37,0:25:09.16,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,lf l don't do it, then who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.54,0:25:13.60,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Then do it yourself! lt's revenge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.04,0:25:17.24,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Don't have other people do it! You\Nshould have raped me yourself!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.01,0:25:21.81,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Shut up! l said don't talk back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.42,0:25:24.28,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,You have no right to talk back!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.15,0:25:27.09,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Fuck me then! Rape me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.65,0:25:29.38,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,You know that's what\Nyou really want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.22,0:25:33.66,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you hate\Nour father, no matter how many\Ntimes you call me a whore...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.46,0:25:36.33,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,The same blood runs through your veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.06,0:25:41.02,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,You must feel pleasure from\Ndoing things that are sinful too!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.77,0:25:42.43,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.65,0:26:37.32,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,l should have done this in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.43,0:26:41.72,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,Next will be those four...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.43,0:26:44.56,Subtitle Style3,,0,0,0,,After them ...